replies.body:
Idk man. My life seems to be on a good track. Got a great paying job in data and security and I run my own job sites.  Looking to start a side business as well. Live with my gf of 5 years. Kid on the way. Got pets. Live in the chaos of new Jersey and work in  the madhouse of New York. It takes me up to two hours to get to work. I'm only 29 so I don't know what you consider being an adult. But I still manage 15+ games a week and have plenty to of free time to study and teach myself 3d design. And down in low elo, games still last at least 30 minutes and I wish they'd last longer. 

But hey, if all that means I'm doing something wrong with my life then fucking up feels pretty good. 
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
